      "content": "it just feels so heavy though. like if nothing is permanent, then all the pain and the daily grind is just... noise. why do we have to endure the noise for so long just to reach the same inevitable nothingness that's waiting for us anyway? it feels like there's no real logic to keeping the struggle going.",
